'''帕夏汗大学袭击事件'''，是指2016年1月20日发生在[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]{{link-en|查尔萨达|Charsadda}}{{link-en|帕夏汗大学|Bacha Khan University}}发生的袭击事件。事件共造成至少22人死亡、超过20人受伤<ref name="cnn">[http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/20/asia/pakistan-university-militant-attack/ At least 22 killed in attack on Bacha Khan University in Pakistan] {{Wayback|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/20/asia/pakistan-university-militant-attack/ |date=20171122075046 }}, [[CNN|CNN]], 21 January 2016</ref><ref name="trib">{{Cite web|title = LIVE: Seven killed, 12 injured as gunmen attack Bacha Khan University in Charsadda – The Express Tribune|url = http://tribune.com.pk/story/1030820/gunfire-heard-at-bacha-khan-university-in-charsadda/|website = The Express Tribune|accessdate = 20 January 2016|language = en-US|archive-date = 2018-12-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226161828/https://tribune.com.pk/story/1030820/gunfire-heard-at-bacha-khan-university-in-charsadda/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title =巴基斯坦大学遇袭事件死亡人数升至21人|url =http://news.southcn.com/international/content/2016-01/20/content_141174979.htm|website =南方网|accessdate =2016-01-20|archive-date =2016-02-02|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160202150035/http://news.southcn.com/international/content/2016-01/20/content_141174979.htm|dead-url =no}}</ref>。[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]称对此袭击负责，但后来其发言人否认负责此次袭击，并予以谴责<ref name=AlJazeera>{{cite news|title=Gunmen storm university in northwest Pakistan|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/01/pakistan-university-charsadda-attacked-160120051953360.html|accessdate=2016-01-20 |publisher=Al Jazeera|date=2016-01-20 |archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225032805/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/01/pakistan-university-charsadda-attacked-160120051953360.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
===袭击背景===
{{Further|巴基斯坦西北部战争}}
巴基斯坦近年来遭到军事暴力袭击，已经有多名激进分子被杀害或发动[[镇压|镇压]]后被拘捕<ref name=dailymail>{{cite news|title=30 dead as gunmen open fire on students at Pakistan university|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3407798/Gunmen-storm-Bacha-Khan-University-Pakistan-firing-students-teachers.html|accessdate=20 January 2016|newspaper=[[每日邮报|每日邮报]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108095329/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3407798/Gunmen-storm-Bacha-Khan-University-Pakistan-firing-students-teachers.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在20世纪初塔利班控制了[[斯瓦特县|斯瓦特县]]山谷后，当地教育机构已经多次遭到了武装分子的袭击<ref>{{cite book|last1=O'Malley|first1=Brendan|title=Education under attack – 2010|date=2010|publisher=[[UNESCO|UNESCO]]|isbn=923104155X}}</ref>。巴基斯坦为争取女性教育而闻名的活动家[[马拉拉·尤萨夫扎伊|-{zh-hans:马拉拉·优素福扎伊; zh-hant:馬拉拉·優素福扎伊;zh-tw:馬拉拉·優素福扎伊;zh-cn:马拉拉·尤萨夫扎伊;}-]]曾经多次在其博客谴责塔利班。此前她曾遭到武装分子的袭击，并受到重伤<ref>{{cite book|last1=Bellal|first1=Annyssa|title=The War Report: Armed Conflict in 2014|date=10 December 2015|publisher=[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]|isbn=019107862X|page=224}}</ref>。

在袭击发生前，白沙瓦政府官员相信因为正在计划攻击，当局关闭了一些学校<ref name=BBC/>。

===事发大学===
事发的大学为帕夏汗大學，于2012年建立，该校以一名活躍於1920年代的[[普什圖族|普什圖族]]獨立社運人士和和平主義者{{link-en|汗·阿卜杜勒·加法尔·汗|Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan}}（别名帕夏汗）命名<ref>{{cite news|title=巴基斯坦一大學遇襲 據報已20死|url=http://www.nanzao.com/tc/international/1525de417f4d248/ba-ji-si-tan-yi-da-xue-yu-xi-ju-bao-yi-7-si-20-shang|accessdate=2016年1月20日|newspaper=[[南华早报|南华早报]]中文网|archive-date=2016年2月5日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205011722/http://www.nanzao.com/tc/international/1525de417f4d248/ba-ji-si-tan-yi-da-xue-yu-xi-ju-bao-yi-7-si-20-shang|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==袭击过程==
2016年1月20日上午9:30，四名装备有自杀背心的男子闯入帕夏汗大学的教室和住宿区，向教师和学生开枪<ref>{{cite news|last1=Boone|first1=Jon|title=Pakistan attacks: at least 30 killed in terror raid at Bacha Khan university|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/20/bacha-khan-university-explosions-heard-as-gunmen-attack-pakistan|accessdate=20 January 2016|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|date=20 January 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108190051/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jan/20/bacha-khan-university-explosions-heard-as-gunmen-attack-pakistan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当时，学生和教师在学校参加纪念{{link-en|汗·阿卜杜勒·加法尔·汗|Khan Abdul Ghaffar Khan}}（别名帕夏汗）逝世纪念日的诗歌会。之后大学表示大学没有得到充分保护<ref name=dawn>{{cite news|title=APS mastermind claims Bacha Khan University attack, 21 killed|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1234200/aps-mastermind-claims-bacha-khan-university-attack-21-killed|accessdate=20 January 2016|work=Dawn|location=Pakistan|date=20 January 2016|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225144236/https://www.dawn.com/news/1234200/aps-mastermind-claims-bacha-khan-university-attack-21-killed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

据[[开伯尔-普什图省|开伯尔-普什图省]]卫生部部长称，此次袭击共造成30余人死亡，60人受伤，其中包括学生和助理教授，而60多名学生被获救<ref name="trib" />。另据军方发言人称，有四名枪手当场被击毙<ref name="trib" /><ref name=AlJazeera/><ref name=BBC>{{cite news|title=Pakistan Charsadda: Gun battle rages at university – BBC News|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35359072|accessdate=20 January 2016|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=20 January 2016|language=en-GB|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225032810/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35359072|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=McKirtySafi>{{cite news|last1=McKirty|first1=Euan|last2=Safi|first2=Sophia|title=Pakistan university militant attack – CNN.com|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/01/20/asia/pakistan-university-militant-attack/|accessdate=20 January 2016|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=20 January 2016|archive-date=2018-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225032807/https://www.cnn.com/2016/01/20/asia/pakistan-university-militant-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title = Gunmen attack Pakistan university, kill at least eight people|url = http://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-attacks-university-idUSKCN0UY0C4|agency = Reuters|date = 20 January 2016|access-date = 20 January 2016|archive-date = 2018-12-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181528/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-pakistan-attacks-university-idUSKCN0UY0C4|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Edhi volunteer claims 15 killed in terror attack on Bacha Khan University Charsadda|url = http://www.dawn.com/news/1234200/edhi-volunteer-claims-15-killed-in-terror-attack-on-bacha-khan-university-charsadda|website = Dawn|location = Pakistan|date = 20 January 2016|access-date = 20 January 2016|archive-date = 2018-12-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181531/https://www.dawn.com/news/1234200/edhi-volunteer-claims-15-killed-in-terror-attack-on-bacha-khan-university-charsadda|dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，据开伯尔-普什图省公共卫生工程部长称，当时大学有54名保安人员驻守，有200人在考场进行考试，袭击发生后，所有的人均被救出<ref name=dawn />。而{{link-en|查尔萨达|Charsadda}}教育局表示，当地关闭学校10天<ref name="trib" />。在袭击事件发生后的1月25日，帕夏汗大学在采取严格的安保措施下再次开课<ref>{{Cite web|title =巴基斯坦帕夏汗大学重新开课|url =http://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/2016/01/25/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E5%B8%95%E5%A4%8F%E6%B1%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%BC%80%E8%AF%BE-469433|website =土耳其广播电视总台|accessdate =2016-01-25|deadurl =yes|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160202202054/http://www.trt.net.tr/chinese/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/2016/01/25/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E5%B8%95%E5%A4%8F%E6%B1%97%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E5%BC%80%E8%AF%BE-469433|archivedate =2016-02-02}}</ref>。

==死者==
事件的受害者包括17名学生，两名园丁，一名看守员和一名教授。而在后来的调查显示，有21人被杀害，其中大部分是住在男性宿舍的学生<ref name=bbcvigil>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35368959|title=Pakistan attack: Vigils held for Bacha Khan University dead|date=21 January 2016|accessdate=21 January 2016|work=BBC News|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201162128/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-35368959|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据一名安全官员称，死亡人数将上升至40人<ref name=dailymail/>。

==袭击策划者==
事后，[[巴基斯坦塔利班运动|巴基斯坦塔利班运动]]称对此袭击负责，塔利班領袖[[曼蘇爾|曼蘇爾]]亦通过電話，向[[美聯社|美聯社]]承認責任，表示是要報復近月多名組織成員被當局殺害。但后来其发言人否认负责此次袭击，并谴责襲擊不符合伊斯蘭精神<ref name=AlJazeera/><ref name="now">{{Cite web|title =塔利班官方否認槍襲巴基斯坦大學|url =http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=165876|website =now新闻|accessdate =2016-01-25|archive-date =2021-09-23|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210923235317/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=165876|dead-url =no}}</ref>。

==反应==
===国内===
事发后，巴基斯坦總理[[纳瓦兹·谢里夫|纳瓦兹·谢里夫]]在[[世界经济论坛|世界经济论坛]]上表示对此次襲擊予以谴责，並對遇難者表示哀悼。他承諾會掃除恐怖主義威脅，不會讓死難者白白犧牲<ref name="now"/><ref name=dawn />。巴基斯坦也于1月21日定为[[全国哀悼日|全国哀悼日]]，向袭击事件遇难者哀悼<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3409737/Pakistan-remembers-dead-Vigils-held-day-national-mourning-21-victims-Taliban-university-massacre.html | title=Pakistan remembers its dead: Vigils held on day of national mourning for the 21 victims of Taliban university massacre | date=21 January 2016 | accessdate=22 January 2016 | archive-date=2016-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160131061858/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3409737/Pakistan-remembers-dead-Vigils-held-day-national-mourning-21-victims-Taliban-university-massacre.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===国际===
*{{flag|Philippines}}：[[菲律宾外交部|外交部]]在声明中表示，对此次袭击予以强烈谴责<ref name="pk">{{cite web| url=http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/22-Jan-2016/jordan-saudi-japan-philippines-china-condemn-charsadda-attack| title=Jordan, Saudi, Japan, Philippines, China condemn Charsadda attack| date=22 January 2016| accessdate=22 January 2016| deadurl=yes| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130120545/http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/national/22-Jan-2016/jordan-saudi-japan-philippines-china-condemn-charsadda-attack| archivedate=2016年1月30日}}</ref>。
*{{flag|Japan}}：[[日本首相|首相]][[安倍晋三|安倍晋三]]和[[日本外务大臣|外务大臣]][[岸田文雄|岸田文雄]]也对帕夏汗大学袭击事件予以谴责<ref name="pk"/>。
*{{PRC}}：[[中华人民共和国外交部发言人|外交部发言人]][[洪磊|洪磊]]在例行记者会上表示，中国政府对这一袭击表示强烈谴责。并表示中方坚决反对针对无辜平民的恐怖袭击，支持巴基斯坦打击恐怖主义，维护国家稳定和人民安全<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1333693.shtml| title=2016年1月21日外交部发言人洪磊主持例行记者会| date=2016-01-21| accessdate=2016-01-21| work=中华人民共和国外交部| archive-date=2017-07-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701203157/http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1333693.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*{{CAN}}：外长[[斯特凡·迪翁|斯特凡·迪翁]]在声明中表示，加拿大反对任何形式的恐怖袭击，并对此次事件予以强烈谴责<ref>{{cite web| url=http://news.gc.ca/web/article-en.do?nid=1028799| title=Canada condemns attack in Pakistan| date=January 20, 2016| accessdate=January 20, 2016| work=加拿大政府| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160122162223/http://news.gc.ca/web/article-en.do?nid=1028799| archive-date=2016-01-22| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。
*{{UNO}}：[[联合国秘书长|联合国秘书长]][[潘基文|潘基文]]通过其发言人办公室发表声明，谴责此次事件，并重申受教育权必须得到坚决保护<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/01-21/7725471.shtml| title=潘基文谴责塔利班袭击巴基斯坦帕夏汗大学| date=2016年1月21日| accessdate=2016年1月21日| work=中新网| archive-date=2017年6月13日| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613163141/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/01-21/7725471.shtml| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

